          <span class="situation-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 4.5v15m7.5-7.5h-15" /></svg></span>
        </button>
        <div class="situation-answer">
          <div class="situation-answer-inner">
            <div class="workflow">
              <div class="workflow-step active-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Pillar</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-title">Pillar II — Apex: Own Your Nature</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Tenet</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-title">Tenet IV — Never Shrink. Never Apologize for Strength.</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-body">The pattern you're trapped in is not who you are. It is what you've been doing. There is a difference. Owning that difference is where the fight begins.</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Lineage</div>
                <p class="workflow-quote">"No man is free who is not master of himself."</p>
                <div class="workflow-cite">— Epictetus, Discourses</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step active-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">Your Practice</div>
                <p class="workflow-action">Name it out loud to yourself. Write down what it costs you — daily, weekly, yearly. Choose one hour today to live without it. Then choose the next. If you need professional help, getting it is the strongest thing you can do.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="workflow-links">
