      <h2 class="pillar-name">Live Within Bounds</h2>
      <p class="pillar-tagline">When life shifts and you need to move with it</p>
    </div>

    <div class="situation-grid">

      <div class="situation-card reveal d2">
        <button class="situation-trigger" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="situation-label">"I just got fired."</span>
          <span class="situation-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 4.5v15m7.5-7.5h-15" /></svg></span>
        </button>
        <div class="situation-answer">
          <div class="situation-answer-inner">
            <div class="workflow">
              <div class="workflow-step active-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Pillar</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-title">Pillar III — Control: Live Within Bounds</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Tenet</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-title">Tenet VIII — Redirect Immediately.</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-body">The door closed. The redirect starts the second the door shuts. Not tomorrow. Not next week. Now.</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Lineage</div>
                <p class="workflow-quote">"I didn't fail the test. I just found 100 ways to do it wrong."</p>
                <div class="workflow-cite">— Benjamin Franklin</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step active-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">Your Practice</div>
                <p class="workflow-action">Apply to one job, reach out to one contact, or start one project. Movement kills spiraling.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="workflow-links">
              <a href="/tenets#tenet-viii" class="workflow-link">Read Tenet VIII →</a>
              <a href="/lineage" class="workflow-link">Read the Lineage →</a>
              <a href="/practice" class="workflow-link">Today's Practice →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="situation-card reveal d3">
        <button class="situation-trigger" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="situation-label">"I'm obsessing over something I can't control."</span>
          <span class="situation-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 4.5v15m7.5-7.5h-15" /></svg></span>
        </button>
        <div class="situation-answer">
          <div class="situation-answer-inner">
            <div class="workflow">
              <div class="workflow-step active-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Pillar</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-title">Pillar III — Control: Live Within Bounds</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Tenet</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-title">Tenet VII — Own Only What Is Yours.</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-body">If you can't change it, it's not yours to carry. Holding what isn't yours breaks your hands for the work that is.</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Lineage</div>
                <p class="workflow-quote">"You always own the option of having no opinion. There is never any need to get worked up about things you can't control."</p>
                <div class="workflow-cite">— Marcus Aurelius, Meditations, Book VI</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step active-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">Your Practice</div>
                <p class="workflow-action">Write down what's consuming you. Circle only what you can actually act on. Work on that. Release the rest.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="workflow-links">
              <a href="/tenets#tenet-vii" class="workflow-link">Read Tenet VII →</a>
              <a href="/lineage" class="workflow-link">Read the Lineage →</a>
              <a href="/practice" class="workflow-link">Today's Practice →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="situation-card reveal d4">
        <button class="situation-trigger" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="situation-label">"My plan fell apart and I don't know what to do next."</span>
          <span class="situation-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 4.5v15m7.5-7.5h-15" /></svg></span>
        </button>
        <div class="situation-answer">
          <div class="situation-answer-inner">
            <div class="workflow">
              <div class="workflow-step active-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Pillar</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-title">Pillar III — Control: Live Within Bounds</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Tenet</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-title">Tenet VIII — Redirect Immediately.</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-body">Plans are guesses with conviction. They fall apart. That's the bounds telling you the path was wrong.</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Lineage</div>
                <p class="workflow-quote">"By failing to prepare, you are preparing to fail."</p>
                <div class="workflow-cite">— Benjamin Franklin</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step active-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">Your Practice</div>
                <p class="workflow-action">Stop mourning the old plan. Write three possible next moves. Pick one. Start before midnight.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="workflow-links">
              <a href="/tenets#tenet-viii" class="workflow-link">Read Tenet VIII →</a>
              <a href="/lineage" class="workflow-link">Read the Lineage →</a>
              <a href="/practice" class="workflow-link">Today's Practice →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="situation-card reveal d5">
        <button class="situation-trigger" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="situation-label">"My anxiety is through the roof and I can't shut my brain off."</span>
          <span class="situation-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 4.5v15m7.5-7.5h-15" /></svg></span>
        </button>
        <div class="situation-answer">
          <div class="situation-answer-inner">
            <div class="workflow">
              <div class="workflow-step active-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Pillar</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-title">Pillar III — Control: Live Within Bounds</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Tenet</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-title">Tenet VII — Own Only What Is Yours.</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-body">Anxiety is your mind trying to own everything at once. Most of what you're carrying hasn't happened yet.</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Lineage</div>
                <p class="workflow-quote">"Everything we hear is an opinion, not a fact. Everything we see is a perspective, not the truth."</p>
                <div class="workflow-cite">— Marcus Aurelius, Meditations, Book IV</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step active-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">Your Practice</div>
                <p class="workflow-action">Write down everything racing through your mind. Cross out anything you cannot act on today. What's left is your real list. Start there.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="workflow-links">
              <a href="/tenets#tenet-vii" class="workflow-link">Read Tenet VII →</a>
              <a href="/lineage" class="workflow-link">Read the Lineage →</a>
              <a href="/practice" class="workflow-link">Today's Practice →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="situation-card reveal d6">
        <button class="situation-trigger" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="situation-label">"Everything feels chaotic and out of control."</span>
          <span class="situation-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 4.5v15m7.5-7.5h-15" /></svg></span>
        </button>
        <div class="situation-answer">
          <div class="situation-answer-inner">
            <div class="workflow">
              <div class="workflow-step active-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Pillar</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-title">Pillar III — Control: Live Within Bounds</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Tenet</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-title">Tenet IX — Trust the Bounds.</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-body">Chaos is what it looks like when you're fighting the bounds instead of working within them.</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Lineage</div>
                <p class="workflow-quote">"An investment in knowledge pays the best interest."</p>
                <div class="workflow-cite">— Benjamin Franklin, Poor Richard's Almanack</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step active-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">Your Practice</div>
                <p class="workflow-action">Identify one thing you've been fighting that you cannot change. Accept it. Build around it instead of against it.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="workflow-links">
              <a href="/tenets#tenet-ix" class="workflow-link">Read Tenet IX →</a>
              <a href="/lineage" class="workflow-link">Read the Lineage →</a>
              <a href="/practice" class="workflow-link">Today's Practice →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="situation-card reveal d7">
        <button class="situation-trigger" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="situation-label">"My marriage is falling apart and I don't know how to save it."</span>
          <span class="situation-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 4.5v15m7.5-7.5h-15" /></svg></span>
        </button>
        <div class="situation-answer">
          <div class="situation-answer-inner">
            <div class="workflow">
              <div class="workflow-step active-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Pillar</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-title">Pillar III — Control: Live Within Bounds</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Tenet</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-title">Tenet IX — Trust the Bounds.</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-body">You cannot control another person's heart. You can only control how you show up. That is the bound. Work within it.</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Lineage</div>
                <p class="workflow-quote">"The universe is change; our life is what our thoughts make it."</p>
                <div class="workflow-cite">— Marcus Aurelius, Meditations, Book IV</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step active-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">Your Practice</div>
                <p class="workflow-action">Write down what is within your control in this marriage and what is not. Work only on your side of the line. You cannot force another person's choices.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="workflow-links">
              <a href="/tenets#tenet-ix" class="workflow-link">Read Tenet IX →</a>
              <a href="/lineage" class="workflow-link">Read the Lineage →</a>
              <a href="/practice" class="workflow-link">Today's Practice →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
