                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Pillar</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-title">Pillar IV — Death: Return to the Whole</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Tenet</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-title">Tenet X — Live Like You Will Die. Because You Will.</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-body">You don't have time. Nobody does. "Someday" is a lie you tell yourself to stay comfortable.</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Lineage</div>
                <p class="workflow-quote">"Think of yourself as dead. You have lived your life. Now, take what's left and live it properly."</p>
                <div class="workflow-cite">— Marcus Aurelius, Meditations, Book VII</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step active-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">Your Practice</div>
                <p class="workflow-action">Do the thing you've been postponing. The one that just came to mind when you read this. Do it today.</p>
