                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Tenet</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-title">Tenet XII — Build a Legacy That Stands in This Life.</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-body">Purpose isn't found. It's built. Purpose follows action, not the other way around.</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Lineage</div>
                <p class="workflow-quote">"If you would not be forgotten as soon as you are dead, either write things worth reading or do things worth the writing."</p>
                <div class="workflow-cite">— Benjamin Franklin, Poor Richard's Almanack</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step active-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">Your Practice</div>
                <p class="workflow-action">Do one thing that benefits someone who will never thank you for it. That's legacy in its smallest, truest form.</p>
              </div>
