                <div class="workflow-step-title">Tenet X — Live Like You Will Die. Because You Will.</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-body">Depression is real. It is not a character flaw. If you need professional help, get it. That is owning your outcome. But you are still here — and the smallest act of living on purpose is a rebellion against the numbness.</div>
